      • distance

        public double distance(Rectangle r)
        Description copied from interface: Geometry

        Returns the distance to the given Rectangle. For a Rectangle this might be Euclidean distance but for an EPSG4326 lat-long Rectangle might be great-circle distance. The distance function should satisfy the following properties:

        distance(r) >= 0

        if r1 contains r2 then distance(r1)<=distance(r2)

        Specified by:
        distance in interface Geometry
        Parameters:
        r - rectangle to measure distance to
        Returns:
        distance to the rectangle r from the geometry
